ng data, posing significant privacy risks. Differential privacy (DP) has emerged as a principled framework that limits the influence of individual data points during training, yet the relationship betwee...", "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2605.11195", "source": "arXiv NLP", "image": "https://arxiv.org/html/2605.11195v1/2605.11195v1/x1.png", "score": 10}]}